Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:14.97,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\0\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:15.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:19.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:23.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:26.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:30.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:33.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:36.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:40.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:44.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:48.40,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:51.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:54.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:59.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:02.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:11.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:13.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:15.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:18.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.38,0:01:22.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The secret organization Shocker,\Nin their quest for world domination,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.89,0:01:27.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,chose professional wrestler Kusaka Noboru\Nto become a fusion of human and pirasaurus,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,a monster capable of killing\Na woolly mammoth in seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:32.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Noboru's little brother Kiyoshi\Nhas been searching fervently for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:34.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,unaware that he has been\Nturned into a merciless cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:37.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now, the cyborg Noboru\NKusaka has appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:40.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in the ring as the mysterious\Npro wrestler Satan Mask,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.73,0:01:44.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and the boy Kiyoshi pursues him,\Nconvinced Satan Mask is his big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:48.86,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,200.389)}Deathmatch in the Ring
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:48.86,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(522,647)}Defeat! Pirasaurus
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Try me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultra Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Running, are you, Kamen Rider?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not running.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just putting off the match until\NI can find out what you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother.\NYou can't stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Kiyoshi.\NJust drop it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep telling you,\NSatan Mask isn't your brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see it in his eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:03:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being pretty\Nstubborn about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta say, I dig it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But seriously, think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Satan Mask is from\NAmerica, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother could've gone to\NAmerica without telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give up until I see\Nunderneath Satan Mask's mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.62,0:03:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, oh boy. Kids these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll help you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.34,0:03:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a real feast\Nfor you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they fall asleep\Nwhile they were waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Did those kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro... you got me this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Satan Mask is in\Nroom 1742 in this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But how are we\Nsupposed to get inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I have my ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now wait for my next trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you get those keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what Mr. Taki said?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,These keys can open up any door!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna yell at you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When he hears I'm doing it for a\Nfriend, he'll forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the mean lady who\Nwouldn't let me see my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So if she's out of the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That means Satan Mask\Nis alone in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great news for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to that snoring!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother snored really\Nbad, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold your horses already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're about to find\Nout if it's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Just be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Satan Mask fans\Nwho want an autograph, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah! We want an autograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You're not the\Nreal Satan Mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kiyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up on this already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a little slow\Non the uptake...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It went perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we can't rest easy yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need to silence that\Nchild for good sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... where is Pirasaurus?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,As planned,\Nhe's gone to test the death mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's\Nkeeping Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not right to break\Na promise to a lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should call him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to look cool\Nwith just women around...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:28.70,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H2A2AEA&}Public Phone
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You go in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really not funny, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What I've come for is your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi? Hey, is Hayato with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen Hayato all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr.\NChairman, it's Mari and Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two? Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know why those kids\Neven joined the racing club!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see the generation\Ngap at play.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You can give the Chairman\Na message from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him we joined the racing\Nclub to improve our figures!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You will all become guinea\Npigs to test my death mist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:16.65,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H2A2AEA&}Public Phone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that just so rude?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put everything on\NHayato's tab tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bartender!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have a soft\Ndrink and a rice bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's like everyone\Nfell right to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Mr. Bartender?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, talk to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari, Yuri, speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They're pretty cute\Nwhen they're asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:09:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're weird, Mr. Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have daughters of my\Nown, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true, what they saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't talk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we go into the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, look after\Nthem, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's clear that Shocker's\Npulling the strings here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost exactly like an\Nincident two weeks ago in Kawasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The one where everyone on a bus\Nwas bleached down to their bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.78,0:10:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.82,0:10:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not sure how things\Nwill develop from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that pro wrestler's role in\Nthings that's tripping you up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's really Kiyoshi's\Nbrother, that complicates things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Better give it a rest before\Nsomething worse happens to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.26,0:10:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You only made it out alive\Nbecause you're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more than luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just more\Ncareful than most.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what did you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do with these?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoshi just wouldn't lay off...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted to see behind\NSatan Mask's mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a real pack of\Ndaredevils in this club, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It really wasn't him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It was someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So Satan Mask wasn't\NKiyoshi's brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't the professional\Nwrestler Kusaka Noboru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kiyoshi said he wasn't the\NSatan Mask from the ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't the Satan\NMask from the ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Satan Mask I saw yesterday\Nisn't the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The eyes under the mask\Nweren't the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirasaurus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're becoming famous all over the\Nworld under your pro wrestling identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The people go into a frenzy\Nover your superhuman feats.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And today, Pirasaurus will fight the\Ntitle match for the championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The arena will be\Npacked with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Among them will be important members of\Nthe Japanese political and economic worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll murder them all in\Nseconds using the death mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan will fall into chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And Shocker will use that\Nchaos to take control of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, cyborg champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The poison gas my body emits can\Nkill tens of thousands at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The champion...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:12.47,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... I'll tail him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you get to do everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also the woman.\NYou can have her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still a member of Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll\Ninfiltrate the hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Kiyoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were waiting for Satan\NMask, I'm afraid he just drove off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.45,0:14:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But that wasn't the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! That's the real one there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you would, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Kiyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Kiyoshi.\NYou're a big boy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I have a favor to\Nask, man to man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Quietly follow that Satan\NMask to his destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he's arrived,\Ncall the Tachibana Racing Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the Tachibana Racing Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.59,0:15:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Satan Mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.04,0:15:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.26,0:15:28.98,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Foolish people...\Nlining up for the executioner's block.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.05,0:15:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself, Ichimonji Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you would follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know who you really\Nare, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The pro wrestler Satan Mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really the Shocker\Ncyborg, Pirasaurus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive, Ichimonji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:15:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And prove your worth to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A sold-out house of fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,As we hoped, it's full of people from the\NJapanese political and economic worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The champion...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Five minutes from now,\Nthe bell will ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The infernal bell that will\Nlead them to their deaths!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirasaurus...\Njust what are you after?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato! He's a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.02,0:17:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then where's the\Nreal Pirasaurus?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the club.\NI'll take over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late... too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirasaurus will already be in the\Narena, slaughtering the Japanese elite!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.23,0:17:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Go to it, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no accounting\Nfor taste...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,People really think he's cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoshi,\Ndon't tell me you still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,One minute until the bell rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirasaurus is at the arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,One minute until the bell\Nrings to start the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for\Ntoday's main event.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.44,0:19:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A 61-minute best out of three!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In the red corner,\Nthe World Ocean Champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,At 230 pounds, Satan Mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And the challenger...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirasaurus...\Nyour challenger is the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, evacuate the arena!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not safe here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops! Where's Kiyoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost sight of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing\Nto my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not safe! Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop being\Nmean to my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.37,0:21:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoshi... look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.83,0:21:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.15,0:21:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Get him away! It's gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.35,0:21:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.35,0:21:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The death mist!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.69,0:22:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't work on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.78,0:22:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you\Nused up your stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.10,0:22:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultra Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.40,0:22:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.53,0:22:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I won! I'm... the champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that\Nmonster was my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.10,0:23:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.37,0:23:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster's death has brought\Nyour brother back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.49,0:23:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.50,0:23:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.52,0:23:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.15,0:23:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They left without us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.12,0:23:40.87,Cont,,0,0,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,510)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:43.35,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:45.05,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.05,0:23:46.78,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,is the fossil man, Hitodanger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.78,0:23:49.74,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Fossil man Hitodanger\Nrepels the Rider Kick,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.74,0:23:52.63,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,and flies like a ninja\Nstar to attack our Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.63,0:23:54.89,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Hitodanger wreaks havoc in the\Nrapids deep in the mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.89,0:23:56.62,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,where he clashes\Nwith Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.62,0:23:59.67,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for\N"Fossil Man Hitodanger."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.01,0:24:00.93,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(400.117,210.389)}Fossil Man
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.01,0:24:00.93,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(717.167,370.389)}Hitodanger
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:10.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.38,0:24:13.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.39,0:24:15.35,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.35,0:24:18.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.89,0:24:20.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.77,0:24:22.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.65,0:24:24.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.44,0:24:25.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.23,0:24:28.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.32,0:24:33.99,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.99,0:24:37.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.58,0:24:41.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.67,0:24:45.42,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Deathmatch in the Ring!\NDefeat Pirasaurus!